Interface IChemFormatMatcher

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface IChemFormatMatcher
extends IChemFormat
    This interface is used for classes that are able to match a certain chemical file format. For example: Chemical Markup Language, PDB etc.
    Author:
    Egon Willighagen
    Created on:
    2004-10-25
